content.p: UNM-Industry Engagement Day was initiated as UNM would like to seek for University-Industry Partnership and Engagement by proactive networking approach with external stakeholders from the industries, local authorities, and University of Nottingham alumnus. Additionally, the event will create a platform to showcase active researchers to engage potential collaborations and to appreciate the existing industrial collaborators. Date: 17 June 2023 Venue: DoubleTree by Hilton Johor Bahru Contact: FOSE.Outreach@nottingham.edu.my This is a private/invitation-only event.
